         <Docu><![CDATA[This function configures the Connection Pool for the specified datasource for the specified JDBC Provider. 

Note, that the action uses the function 'configureDSConnectionPool' of Wsadminlib.

If parameter 'Host' is not provided, the local WebSphere installation is targeted.

If parameteres 'Username' and 'Password' are not provided the WebSphere security has to be turned off.]]></Docu>
